The user created a page that contained import macros that inmport themselves. 
The java virtual machine will terminate with a segmentation violation. The 32 bit java will continue with an error message while the 64bit JVM crashed. This can be replicated in update 18 and update 17.

# Add a task list using the macro browser (wiki editor).
# Add a custom title. 
# Insert macro

This adds the following macro:
{code}
{tasklist:title=Test}{tasklist}
{code}

The {{title}} property has no effect.

Adding the macro manually like this:
{code}
{tasklist:Test}{tasklist}
{code}

creates a task list with title *Test*.

